iv><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y89 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">是再过<span class="_ _13"> </span>20<span class="_ _13"> </span>年，就会步入人生的后半程，那个时候，如果你</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y8a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">有禅修的习惯，不仅不会孤独，大脑也不容易衰退。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 hd y93 ffc fs3 fc0 sc1 ls16 ws0">4.治愈疾病 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
